# Hype KOL Dashboard — Environment Variables
#
# This project uses lark-cli (via @larksuite/cli npm package) for all
# Lark Base data access. No HTTP API server required.
#
# Required:
LARK_BASE_TOKEN=your-lark-base-token-here
#
# Optional (for TikTok embed features):
# TIKTOK_API_KEY=your-tiktok-api-key
#
# Optional (for development):
# NODE_ENV=development
